parent.title: Evermore
parent.description: When the king of Evermore weds his new queen, beautiful elf princesses Leena and Zara (Agatha Vega and Sophie Reade) become new stepsisters and the only heirs to the throne. The peaceful kingdom is thrown into chaos when vengeful sorceress Arrix (Valentina Nappi) fulfills an ancient prophecy, summoning an army of Hellions who will stop at nothing to dispose of the royal family and bring her the crown. After the Hellions storm the castle, brave warriors Leena and Zara go on the run and team up with a talented rogue and a sorcerer’s apprentice (Xander Corvus and Danny D), putting their sword fighting skills and magical powers to the test as they attempt to foil Arrix’s sinister plan.
